                Dear <$client.tForWhomUserInfo.First_Name>,
            </p>
            <p id="content-2">
                It is my pleasure to extend to you a formal offer to join Precise Systems, Inc. ("Precise Systems") as <span class="article-content"><$client.tEventCategories_Category_16.Value></span> <$client.env.eval(client.tForWhomUserInfo.Functional_Role.length()>0?' - <$client.tForWhomUserInfo.Functional_Role>':'')>. Since 1990, Precise Systems has worked to establish a significant presence in the Defense industry.  We are extremely proud of our reputation for excellence among our customers and work diligently to guard it.  This superb reputation is directly linked to the outstanding quality of our work and our people.  Those who know you, or who have met you, are impressed with your achievements, credentials, and your potential to contribute to the future success of our company.  
            </p>
            <p id="content-3">
                When you join us, you will be reporting to <$client.tEventManagers_Person_1.First_Name> <$client.tEventManagers_Person_1.Last_Name>. Your base hourly rate will be $<$client.tForWhomUserInfo.Hourly_Rate> per hour and you will be compensated for every hour worked. In the event that you exceed forty (40) hours in a week you will be compensated at a time and a half rate. It is anticipated that you will work 40 hours per week.  Salary differentials apply to Shift 2 and Shift 3 for hours beyond normal business hours (6:00 a.m. through 6:00 p.m.)  You will work <$client.tForWhomUserInfo.Shift>. Your start date will be <span class="long-date"><$client.tEventDates_Date_2.Value></span>.  
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-10">
        <div class="col-lg-12 table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-bordered table-condensed">
